Rompebolas
==========
Simple Qt game based on SameGame. Work in progress :)

![Rompebolas screenshot](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LeandroGuillen/rompebolas/master/pantallazo.png "Rompebolas in full glory")

To build it:
```
make
```

To run it:
```
./rb
```
